  "prompt": "Which are the good CA coaching centres in south Delhi?",
  "response": "As of my last update, several reputed CA coaching centers in South Delhi are known for their quality instruction and successful student track records. Here are a few you might consider:\n\n1. **IMS Proschool** - Known for its comprehensive programs, including CA Foundation, Intermediate, and Final courses.\n\n2. **Aldine CA** - Offers innovative and interactive classes, and their faculty includes some well-known names in CA coaching.\n\n3. **Vidya Sagar Institute (VSI)** - Has a strong track record of students clearing the CA exams, particularly in the Foundation and Intermediate levels.\n\n4. **ETEN CA** - Offers both face-to-face and satellite classes, designed to help students understand and crack the CA exams.\n\n5. **EduEx** - Provides a range of courses and a structured learning environment for CA aspirants.\n\n6. **Mohit Agarwal Classes** - Known for its focus on personalized attention and comprehensive coverage of the CA syllabus.\n\n7. **KCC Classes** - Offers well-structured programs and access to experienced faculty for all levels of the CA exam.\n\nWhen choosing a coaching center, consider factors such as faculty expertise, past track records, teaching methodology, location, batch size, and fee structure. It's often helpful to visit the centers, attend demo classes if possible, and speak with current or former students to get a better sense of which option might be the best fit for you.",
